name: Dual-Phase Neverlight Cells and Dual-Phase Everlight Cells

imgDesc.text: Dual-Phase Neverlight Cells are receivers for Primal Beams. Compared to normal Neverlight Cells, these require two Primal Beams fired from two Everlight Cells to activate. There exist similar Dual-Phase Everlight Cells that can fire two Primal Beams simultaneously.
